                            <comment id="15009852" author="enis" created="Tue, 17 Nov 2015 23:42:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We need the leases mechanism in the REST scan resources as well. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;One open question is given stateless scanners, should statefull scanners be deprecated and removed or not? &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15010046" author="apurtell" created="Wed, 18 Nov 2015 02:19:13 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;One open question is given stateless scanners, should statefull scanners be deprecated and removed or not? &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Stateful scanners are by definition not REST-ful. We should have deprecated them when stateless scanners were added, in retrospect.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adding leases in the meantime before removal is no less problematic than their existence in the first place. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15010048" author="apurtell" created="Wed, 18 Nov 2015 02:21:45 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;We should have deprecated them when stateless scanners were added, in retrospect.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

